{"tid":1406844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 不是割蓆 ] 唔好係自己防線內放火，記住諗清楚行動效果。","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:33:04.000Z","uid":257422,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16288441fbb6c5d45131756ac8039ce1fe94fadd","tid":1406844,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"純粹提醒一下，<br />\n頭先見d火種跌左係自己防線內，<br />\n但義士都繼續加大火勢，最後只係燒到等消防救，暫時睇真係未見到行動目的，記住義士當下果刻真係要諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而記住除左策略、效果上既問題<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦記住最緊要最緊要唔好整傷自己人</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n記住8月5日罷工罷市課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5e61096645e89995a4a262e976a6f728633c31","tid":1406844,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72c61e07c9d5acaee34611f05f852b39dab1178","tid":1406844,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"記住要小心就得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/